body:
With this pack installed, dispensers and dropper are altered to be more consistent with observers, including the directional indicators being present in only two sides of the block even when rotated vertically, and the removal of the "vertical" version of their front textures.

I have a different project that alters the observer instead, if you believe you would prefer that style, click the following link: [Consistent Sentries: Dispenser Style](https://modrinth.com/project/consistent-sentries-dispenser-style)

**Extra details**
- the current version of the pack is compatible with 1.21.9 to 26.1;
- the zip file can just be dragged and dropped in your "resourcepacks" folder, unzipping isn't required;
